{"tid":749066,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下如果想辦義教既話可以點搞","createTime":"2018-07-19T16:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T05:02:51.000Z","uid":15691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77946182b200565f4200bfe38bbdb392eeae3168","tid":749066,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"都教左十年水<br />\n眼見而家個泳圈風氣愈黎愈偏向利益為主而非學術傳承<br />\n好多唔識教，教錯野，連水都唔識游走出黎呃飯食<br />\n只要宣傳做得體面 大把家長學生仆倒去<br />\n<br />\n我主要想幫下啲基層或者好難接觸呢方面運動既人士<br />\n或者好多年都好怕水唔敢踏出第一步去接觸既人<br />\n希望可以幫多啲人 將我既知識同經驗傳播開去<br />\n<br />\n1. 想問下可以點樣舉辦呢類義教？<br />\n2. 有冇機構會有funding 支持？<br />\n3. 有冇巴打有興趣一齊參與？<br />\n<br />\n利申 非social撚 好怕接觸啲要social懶係talkative既活動<br />\n<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"2ff6545f16ee4e897dd1ccf580416f2f86ded3b6","tid":749066,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<br />\n<br />\nps 我知義務補習有 陳校長義免費補習天地，都係會幫基層嘅小朋友，巴打可以唸唸"},{"pid":"1919160f7c03aa5a7b3a126280a86be442f40491","tid":749066,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T04:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d426b442a43390931ec094c4b56c30453ffe25","tid":749066,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:22:31.000Z","msg":"想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學過一次 好怕浸親 學唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe3933517d688bf440a7ce47c185d5ac8fca2b9","tid":749066,"uid":15691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39d426b442a43390931ec094c4b56c30453ffe25","tid":749066,"uid":14214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T19:22:31.000Z","msg":"想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學過一次 好怕浸親 學唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"